Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.34,0:00:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.61,0:00:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's neither a circus, nor a musical.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.01,0:00:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a magic show either.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.83,0:00:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is the best entertainment \Nshow in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.31,0:00:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there was a girl who aspired to join\Nthis Kaleido Stage and got the leading role.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.19,0:00:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is Sora Naegino, 16 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.69,0:00:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the stage she dreamed of\Nwas taken away by a certain person.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.14,0:00:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would Sora and her friends be\Nable to get Kaleido Stage back?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.73,0:00:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tattoo Kiss hajimari wa \Naka to kuro no Passion{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.06,0:01:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Toki ni urahara na kokoro o tayori ni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.39,0:01:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tattoo Kiss kirifuda wa mirai o kaeru Mission{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.64,0:01:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Koi ni aimai na kotae wa iranai {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.67,0:01:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Arienai genjitsu minai furi shite mo Bet{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.23,0:01:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Egatai shinjitsu\NCan U feel me now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.02,0:01:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nesshiyasui jibun ni Say What? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.37,0:01:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tomadou iibun {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.37,0:01:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dreamin' samenai yume ochiteku sadame{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.97,0:01:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't stop lovin' Can't stop lovin' U\NYa ya ya{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.28,0:02:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Believe in U hikikae ni subete ushinatte mo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.11,0:02:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Still lovin' Can't stop lovin' U\NNo no no{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.84,0:02:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tattoo Kiss {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.12,0:02:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.12,0:02:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the spirit of the stage who\Ncan only be seen by chosen ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.32,0:02:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora Naegino is the only one who can see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.29,0:02:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With her efforts and inborn spirit,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.93,0:02:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she steadily climbed the ladder to be a star.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.25,0:02:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And finally, she realized a\Nco-performance with Layla, the top star.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.70,0:02:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While Kaleido Stage was\Nenjoying its big surge in popularity,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.97,0:02:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora and her friends experienced ordeals\Nwhich they'd never encountered before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.87,0:03:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The treacherous Yuri Killian.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.35,0:03:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The current Kaleido Stage will\Nbe dissolved after today's show.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.08,0:03:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.71,0:03:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaleido Stage will be dissolved?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.92,0:03:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They could not believe\Ntheir ears, but it was fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.93,0:03:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kaleido Stage was to be\Nbought out and immediately disbanded.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.41,0:03:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the mastermind\Nbehind it all was Yuri Killian.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.56,0:03:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri was a star at Kaleido Stage,\Nsharing the popularity with Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.52,0:03:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he had been secretly planning a takeover.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.82,0:03:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won. I defeated Kalos.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.66,0:03:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the last show near at hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.42,0:03:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora tried to tell Kalos, the owner,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.78,0:03:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,how she felt about this performance, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.10,0:03:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although today is our last show...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.14,0:03:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... {\i1}Because {\i0}it's the last show,\Nlet's make it the best show.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.18,0:03:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss, do you have anything\Nyou want me to tell everybody?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.82,0:04:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is one thing I want to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.25,0:04:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to prepare yourself for\Nthe stage like that, it's better not to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.22,0:04:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.73,0:04:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora could not hide her agitation\Nafter the way Kalos brushed her off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.82,0:04:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, shortly afterwards,\Nshe even lost the ability to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.45,0:04:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.09,0:04:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have something I want you to listen to!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.31,0:04:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.51,0:04:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.55,0:04:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.69,0:04:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost the ability to see Fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.72,0:04:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, if you can see me,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.70,0:04:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it means that you were chosen for the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.82,0:04:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once, there was a man who was able to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.78,0:04:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man I was talking about\Ngradually lost the ability to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.84,0:04:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Sora lost everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.24,0:04:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}--Everything is gone all at once.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.63,0:04:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--and she didn't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.40,0:04:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't know what I should do at all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.43,0:04:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words which cleared up her confusion
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.15,0:04:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,came unexpectedly from Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.73,0:05:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how hard you guys try,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.77,0:05:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your Kaleido Stage will be over after today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.40,0:05:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not thinking that today is the last day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.36,0:05:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.61,0:05:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look at the reality, Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.04,0:05:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if Kaleido Stage closes its doors,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.37,0:05:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it can't close the door to my future.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.69,0:05:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will not be my last \Nshow, unless I wish it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.09,0:05:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least, if I couldn't believe that,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.00,0:05:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't appear on this stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.24,0:05:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.29,0:05:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, today is not the end of the show, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.96,0:05:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to appear on the stage\Nmany more times with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.63,0:05:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.92,0:05:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The curtain will be raised as scheduled.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.28,0:05:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.29,0:05:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe, I don't want to lose... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.85,0:05:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't want to lose the partner\Nwho motivates me so much...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.61,0:06:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.59,0:06:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.79,0:06:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She messed up her makeup right now, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.14,0:06:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is fixing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.38,0:06:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.34,0:06:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Miss Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.14,0:06:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... I'm doing my best to hurry, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.93,0:06:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.52,0:06:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will do it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.52,0:06:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.93,0:06:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Miss Layla...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.54,0:06:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk. I can't do my work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.05,0:06:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I enjoyed co-starring on stage with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.33,0:06:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Miss Layla... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.76,0:06:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why would you say something like that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.83,0:06:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is not the end, right? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.46,0:06:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it looks good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.61,0:06:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.32,0:06:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.24,0:06:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you see me again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.14,0:07:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, unfortunately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.46,0:07:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.57,0:07:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card represents a hope for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.65,0:07:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A hope for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.56,0:07:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.02,0:07:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.08,0:07:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Starting tomorrow, our \Nperformance will start!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.65,0:07:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, the curtain was\Ndropped on the last show
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.06,0:07:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,while everyone's hearts were\Nfilled with mixed emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, each member\Nstarted walking their own path.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.45,0:07:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing how time passes by so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.48,0:07:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--And yet, not only are we far from \Ncreating our own Kaleido Stage,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.82,0:07:33.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--To shine on that brilliant \Nstage once again:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.87,0:07:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--but also we have no jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.89,0:07:35.45,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--with that wish firmly in their minds,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.45,0:07:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they trained on their own every day\Nand worked hard at part-time jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.00,0:07:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There, there, there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.03,0:07:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, Layla appeared in a\Nmovie, influenced in part by her father.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.91,0:07:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.45,0:07:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Each of them was living a new life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.29,0:07:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One day, Sora and her friends got a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.62,0:08:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found you a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.06,0:08:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.40,0:08:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.70,0:08:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Wanted: performers to perform\Non the open stage at Marine Park"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.12,0:08:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The scale of the stage was small,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.52,0:08:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they'd be able to appear on stage again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.59,0:08:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got some e-mail responses.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.33,0:08:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.50,0:08:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.41,0:08:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're coming in!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.02,0:08:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.48,0:08:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, all the old friends gathered,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.11,0:08:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they formed a new group, Freedom Lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.18,0:08:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then came the date that they performed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.71,0:08:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora and her friends put\Non a wonderful performance
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.83,0:08:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as if they were trying to\Nvent all their frustrations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their performance was a great success.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.75,0:08:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But somehow,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.80,0:08:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora felt something was missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.23,0:08:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If Miss Layla were here with us...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.38,0:08:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as she thought that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.61,0:08:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.47,0:08:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.86,0:09:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A mysterious Masked Star appeared\Nand flew freely through the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.56,0:09:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She showed off an amazing performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.01,0:09:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.49,0:09:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's amazing. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.82,0:09:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She nailed everyone's \Nattention in an instant.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.08,0:09:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to this mysterious\NMasked Star's performance,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.51,0:09:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Marine Park was packed day after day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.18,0:09:40.92,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--We have plenty of time until\Nthe Masked Star's show starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.25,0:09:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Sora's group's performance was\Nalso garnering favorable reviews.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.65,0:09:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then one day, an incident happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.06,0:09:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't miss that photo op.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.82,0:09:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.45,0:09:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Masked Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.68,0:09:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.23,0:09:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Masked Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.08,0:09:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A young brother and sister\Nclimbed up on a steel tower
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.46,0:09:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--in order to have a better look at the Masked Star's performance.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.36,0:09:55.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--Be a big girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.64,0:09:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.26,0:10:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call a rescue team quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.63,0:10:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.68,0:10:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Melissa, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.29,0:10:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.84,0:10:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The way she moves... She must be..."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.04,0:10:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora was convinced.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.85,0:10:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.75,0:10:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's going to crash!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.53,0:10:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.29,0:10:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.65,0:11:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.13,0:11:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora avoided a disaster working\Nin combination with the Masked Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.03,0:11:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I believe that the Masked Star is Miss Layla.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.97,0:11:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If Miss Layla is with us, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.52,0:11:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I think creating our own\NKaleido Stage is possible.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.77,0:11:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.21,0:11:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri's never-ending evil schemes\Nstruck at Sora and her friends once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.78,0:11:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And finally, the Masked\NStar's identity was disclosed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.74,0:11:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After Yuri's interference forced Sora\Nand her friends out of Marine Park,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.65,0:11:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as their final hope, they decided to enter\Nthe world performance festival in Vancouver.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.85,0:11:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.73,0:11:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we get a good reputation, Marine\NPark's owner may reconsider firing us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.89,0:11:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, Layla was working her way through\Nplaying the lead role of the movie in London.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.40,0:11:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.70,0:11:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice to hear the movie\Nshoot is going smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.71,0:12:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The success of this movie will\Ndecide your future. It's very important.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.28,0:12:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.05,0:12:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the end of next week,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.52,0:12:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll finally shoot the big climax scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.01,0:12:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you success.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.03,0:12:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.65,0:12:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then came the date for the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.38,0:12:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.20,0:12:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Z"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.73,0:12:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Waiting for Sora and her Freedom Lights
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.20,0:12:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was the local amateur group "Z",
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.10,0:12:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who gave a similar performance \Nto Sora's group's.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.18,0:12:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.65,0:12:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same as ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.07,0:12:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did they copy us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.68,0:12:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.77,0:12:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was also Yuri's scheme.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.63,0:12:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then their lives will be over. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.62,0:12:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're getting wonderful cheers...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.46,0:12:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't afford to be beat by those guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.59,0:13:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just before they were ready to\Nperform, Freedom Lights was cornered.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.88,0:13:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now what are we gonna do? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.79,0:13:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.21,0:13:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will postpone the shoot until next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.93,0:13:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In return, I expect the\Nbest performance out of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.90,0:13:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The person who appeared\Nwas that mysterious Masked Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.66,0:13:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, Sora and her\Nfriends' performance started.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.49,0:13:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Masked Star...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.98,0:13:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.83,0:14:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just when everyone was convinced\Nof Freedom Lights' victory...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.54,0:14:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.08,0:14:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Layla!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.55,0:14:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.01,0:14:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is supposed to be\Nthe day for the climax shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.85,0:14:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked them to postpone the shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.36,0:14:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.18,0:14:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm aware that I'm selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.69,0:15:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I couldn't just stand by and do nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.02,0:15:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to perform a perfect...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.63,0:15:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a perfect performance\Nthat makes me fully satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.88,0:15:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to receive applause that\Nmakes my whole body tremble.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.93,0:15:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And right now, I have a\Npartner who can make it possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.03,0:15:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.74,0:15:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've not finished my last show.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.91,0:15:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, make sure\Nto finish the movie shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.07,0:15:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After that, do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.53,0:15:33.82,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--Miss Layla...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.90,0:15:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Layla decided to appear on stage \Nagain with Sora and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.68,0:15:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--That was when the miracle happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.75,0:15:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.11,0:15:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.39,0:15:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.12,0:15:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.97,0:15:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.90,0:15:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having resolved to live for the stage,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.66,0:15:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she also became able to see me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.48,0:16:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Layla was chosen for the stage just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.27,0:16:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is proof that you can attempt\Nthe legendary great maneuver.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.54,0:16:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The legendary great maneuver?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.82,0:16:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was tried once, a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.30,0:16:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After that, no one has\Nsuccessfully performed that maneuver.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.41,0:16:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One person was frightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.34,0:16:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another tried it recklessly \Nand lost his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.06,0:16:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to attempt that maneuver,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.66,0:16:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you will be the second\Npair to try from Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.14,0:16:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It needs two stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.62,0:16:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to the two\Nwho tried before and failed?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.58,0:16:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They died.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.59,0:16:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... I think I can do it\Nif it's with you, Miss Layla!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.76,0:16:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The two had made up their minds and headed\Nto the Grand Canyon for special training.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.08,0:17:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Waiting there was the one and only person\Nwho knew the legendary great maneuver.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.89,0:17:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome. It's been awhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.28,0:17:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.23,0:17:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.85,0:17:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so began Sora and\NLayla's excruciating ordeal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.04,0:17:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The training they endured every day was hard\Nbeyond anything the two had ever imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.31,0:17:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Contrary to Layla, who steadily managed\Nto finish the assignments she was given,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.46,0:17:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it took all Sora had just to keep up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.73,0:17:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.62,0:17:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla, why won't you say anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.62,0:17:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please say something. Say anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.50,0:17:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have nothing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.79,0:17:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brushed aside by Layla,\Nthe partner she put so much trust in,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.44,0:17:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora's confidence was shaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.45,0:18:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a nuisance if you're going to\Nprepare yourself with a half-baked attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.94,0:18:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If quitting is better for Miss Layla, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.29,0:18:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After Sora lost her confidence,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.97,0:18:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she headed to Layla's room\Nwith her mind set on quitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.15,0:18:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla, I want to talk about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.15,0:18:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.91,0:18:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ken...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.97,0:18:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla is not here right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.47,0:18:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's out running.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.04,0:18:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Running? At a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.49,0:18:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. She's trying to lose weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.64,0:18:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Losing weight?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.97,0:18:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.38,0:18:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The greater the weight difference\Nbetween the two performers,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.60,0:18:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the lower the chance of success\Nof the legendary great maneuver.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.66,0:18:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla is doing all \Nof this because of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.90,0:18:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partners are supposed to be equal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.97,0:18:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Ken.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.00,0:19:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.59,0:19:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.50,0:19:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.77,0:19:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.58,0:19:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because the special\Ntraining is hard and painful,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.94,0:19:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made excuses and told myself that\NI don't have the skills to be your partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.39,0:19:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to run away by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.23,0:19:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.85,0:19:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never doubt myself again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.71,0:19:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll work much harder and catch up to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.47,0:19:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm going to perfect the\Nlegendary great maneuver by any means!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.19,0:19:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We came all this way to do just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.22,0:19:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.10,0:19:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both Sora and Layla\Nrestored their trust in each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.41,0:19:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, God imposed new ordeals on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.32,0:20:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.69,0:20:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.97,0:20:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Due to her drastic weight loss,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.50,0:20:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Layla grew dizzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.79,0:20:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.62,0:20:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Good. She seems to be doing okay.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.39,0:20:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Layla was injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.53,0:20:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What cruel fate awaited them?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.02,0:20:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At last, the time came to show\Nthe results of the special training.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.48,0:20:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, after Layla smashed\Nher right shoulder into the cliff,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.70,0:20:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,her condition worsened.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.12,0:20:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it came to a point that\Nher doctor told her not to perform.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.68,0:20:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, her determination was not shaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.46,0:20:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora and Layla's performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.46,0:20:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, the time was ripe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.25,0:20:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After they overcame cruel ordeals,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.17,0:20:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the time came at last for Sora and Layla\Nto attempt the legendary great maneuver.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.20,0:21:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like they don't have any lifelines.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.11,0:21:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, I'm getting chills.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.66,0:21:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.26,0:21:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.20,0:21:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I need to focus only on Miss Layla.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.40,0:21:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.61,0:21:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jump toward Miss Layla... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.39,0:21:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you have wings on your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.02,0:21:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm not scared at all. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.21,0:21:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm with Miss Layla. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.88,0:21:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm so happy. I feel like crying.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.73,0:21:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wish I could keep\Nperforming like this forever.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.63,0:21:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The brilliance of life that\Ndoesn't flinch at anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.02,0:21:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is indeed the legendary great maneuver.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.81,0:22:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only is the legendary great\Nmaneuver a dangerous maneuver,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.80,0:22:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it is also an expression of a\Nstrong life that keeps even death at bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.59,0:22:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arlon...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.01,0:22:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The maneuver which even gives\Nthe audience the strength to live...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.66,0:22:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what the legendary great maneuver was.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.76,0:22:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it with all our might.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.04,0:22:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.54,0:22:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One! Two! Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.81,0:22:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The applause that Layla had wished for;
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.70,0:22:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the grand applause that\Nmade her whole body tremble.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.42,0:22:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the price for getting\Nthat applause was just too high.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.90,0:22:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the least, I know I won't be able\Nto appear on Kaleido Stage anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.69,0:23:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.25,0:23:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not true, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.43,0:23:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.97,0:23:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaleido Stage had lost Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.82,0:23:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will the fate of Sora and the others be?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.85,0:23:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sekasu you ni muragaru Hard luck{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.13,0:23:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nagasarete Time is over {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.36,0:23:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yokoku doori Take it easy {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.26,0:23:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tsuredasu yo imasugu {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.54,0:23:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hurry up (here we go) {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.27,0:23:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gouin only (saisoku drive) {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.59,0:23:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nichijou miorosu best view {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.02,0:23:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sunset point (favorite) {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.97,0:23:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Harbor light (stormy night) {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.86,0:23:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Asu no tame ni escape {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.45,0:24:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bakansu nashi demo oashisu wa get{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.37,0:24:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Keitai off tte ai o charge shite{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.59,0:24:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yasashisa dake ja iyasenai itami mo aru kara{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.64,0:24:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We are alone. Surechigau{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.02,0:24:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's going on? {\i0}
